description:
This is a 18 minute workout called '15 min Pilates Workout for Beginners' from the channel Flow with Mira.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

This Flow with Mira Pilates Class is perfect to add to your other workouts or done on its own to help you achieve weight loss, a toned tummy, and lean legs. Do this every day and see amazing results!
